| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4764 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1f0391db-b41a-5065-b738-cbfdd5482ed7"
